reviews/originality/2026-05-29-time-is-held-not-counted-a48a2fda9bb1cc91.json:110:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.26. Human-condition fit is direct but narrow: stable adults with deadline stress, rumination, future dread, and achievement-contingent self-worth. It is not for acute panic, trauma activation, severe depression, mania, psychosis, addiction withdrawal, dissociation, or people avoiding concrete obligations. Publishability should stay low unless it is framed as a tested temporal-integration practice rather than a metaphysical discovery.",
