reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:61:- Robert Sharf on mindfulness and Steven Katz on contextualism, PubMed Sharf record https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25361692/ and Katz overview https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/13/10/983: overlap: Close pressure source. They challenge neutral experience models and show how concepts, traditions, rhetoric, and historical forms shape reports and practice meaning.; difference: They do not offer the exact split-source predictive layer test for warnings, repairs, and cross-training failures.; novelty impact: High reduction for report-shaping and context-shaping claims.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:106:Answers that support contribution: Practitioners provide concrete cases where a layer-coded mismatch predicts a repair that a generic technique, tradition, or clinical-risk model misses, for example when a noting-trained student applies deconstructive effort inside direct recognition, or when a Pure Land convert treats nembutsu as self-owned achievement despite instruction to entrust.
reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-does-independently-coded-function-by-placement-analysis-plus-post-gap-ad.md:30:The revision became transformed rather than simply stronger. It no longer argues that every path needs the very self it dissolves in the same structural sense. It now argues that every path must preserve continuity functions, and that traditions differ by how those functions are distributed. That is a better model. It is less brittle, more testable, and more useful for modern practitioners who encounter no-self, surrender, psychedelics, or self-transcendence outside durable containers. The modern human-condition pressure also improved. The revised version names plausible cohorts and correctly excludes acute psychiatric crisis and intact single-lineage settings. Still, the cohort map is too broad. The model is strongest for people facing identity-dissolution pressure without teacher, community, ethical frame, screening, or integration. It is not yet a general model for loneliness, depression, grief, digital comparison, or meaning loss. Its practical value is diagnostic, not devotional or therapeutic by itself. The remaining analytic risk is the receiving surface. Zahavi's minimal self may support the claim that experience has first-personal givenness, but that does not automatically establish the practical capacities of trust, openness, correction, and integration. Those are thicker than pre-reflective givenness and can be socially trained or socially damaged. The model should keep that bridge explicit. Final judgment: the revision is a real improvement because it accepted the distributed-containment challenge and converted the original overstatement into a graded comparative tool. It has not yet earned the status of an architectural law. Its next burden is empirical and coding discipline: show that the function layer predicts something the containment layer cannot.
reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-does-independently-coded-function-by-placement-analysis-plus-post-gap-ad.md:40:**Unresolved crux:** Does independently coded function-by-placement analysis, plus post-gap admissibility grammar, predict screening, sequencing, warnings, verification methods, and failure modes better than container strength, doctrine, institution, practice intensity, clinical vulnerability, and lineage history alone? A second unresolved crux is cohort specificity: the model currently fits destabilization from unsupported self-dissolution better than it fits loneliness, grief, depression, or meaning loss in general.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:31:Structural observation: SN 22.89 already separates a formal path achievement from a remaining gradient: the noble disciple has abandoned lower fetters and does not assume 'I am this,' yet residual 'I am' conceit, desire, and obsession remain until further contemplation uproots them. SN 45.8 gives a clear practitioner-agency grammar for right effort. Tannisho gives the opposite formal marker: entrusting, non-calculation, and Amida's working, while warning against claiming nembutsu as one's own practice. Cross-reading these texts supports the candidate's two-track architecture, but also shows that much of the architecture is already available in primary sources.
