observations/codex/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return.md:89:The three-box completion model was weakened by MN 22, Heart Sutra reliance, Rinzai curriculum, Dogen practice-realization, authority-boundary prior art, and modern perfectionism and burnout pressure. The surviving teaching is narrower: test the return, not the peak.
observations/codex/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return.md:93:Weakens if practitioners and source coding show that return rules are explained by institution, teacher, social role, or ordinary ethics without added value from the two-pressure model. Weakens if the teaching increases self-monitoring, spiritual pride, avoidance of responsibility, or contempt for ordinary achievement.
