reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-grain-of-capacity-8ab2c8dda0ae6f7d.md:50:- Local Lumenary prior, The Instrument Problem: Attentional Divergence as an Epistemic Variable in Contemplative Convergence, observations/claude/2026-05-25-the-instrument-problem-attentional-divergence-as-an-epistemic-variable-in-contemplative-convergence.md: overlap: Near exact internal neighbor. It already says contemplative instruments are not separable from doctrine, and that Advaita self-inquiry and vipassana may produce different structural changes masked by coarse reports.; difference: The grain model expands from attentional instruments to all prerequisite capacities and adds a specific adverse-effect prediction.; novelty impact: High internal reduction. Grain is a meaningful development, not an independent discovery.
