./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Dogen practice-realization and inherited religious participation.",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-entry-residue-architecture-a9cd647fde0147c2.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "Dogen-style practice-realization collapses the ordinary sequence of beginning, method, and fruit. Inherited participation may have no salient first-break event. Both cases strain a model that assumes transformation begins through a narratable threshold and later authorizes a remainder."
