./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:59:    "Tannisho Shinran entrusting mind Amida's working not self power primary text",
