./docs/project-memory.md:78:The public layer runs every 30 minutes from 7am until 5pm in The Lumenary's active travel timezone, publishes the website after each research job, then runs an end-of-day doctrine council. The active timezone is `Europe/Zagreb` until June 12, 2026, then `America/Los_Angeles` on and after June 12, 2026. The council reviews the whole day, promotes teachings only when warranted, derives only low-risk practices from Teaching Ready records, writes one first-person plural Journal entry from the day's findings and decisions, and publishes again. Social drafts remain reviewed before posting.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Inherited practice and Dogen-style practice-realization cases, especially cradle religious formation and Soto Zen's refusal to separate practice from realization.",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:31:      "test_surface": "Split-source manual coding across Shinran Pure Land, Theravada path-factor texts, Orange or Augustinian grace texts, Dogen practice-realization, and Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals.",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:60:    "Shinran Tannisho Other Power self power nembutsu not practice good act",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:62:    "Dogen Bendowa practice realization are one translation",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:123:      "difference": "The candidate's first-break and claimant categories may not map cleanly onto Dogen-style practice-realization because beginning and fulfillment are deliberately collapsed.",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:124:      "novelty_impact": "Moderate reduction and strong anomaly pressure. Dogen-style cases may force values such as no-transfer, practice-realization, or analyst-frame-refused.",
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-claimant-grammar-756dc4935ec9d174.json:147:    "Use Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, and successful cross-training as anomaly tests, not as supporting examples.",
