./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:47:- Tannisho Other Power Original Vow no practice no good teacher maturity faith
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:51:- Prior Lumenary audit, Authority-Boundary Ecology, reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.json, and dialogue Can native verification or authority boundaries be identified non-circularly, findings/convergences/2026-05-26-can-native-verification-or-authority-boundaries-be-identified-non-circularly-acro.md: overlap: Very close. It already says to establish native authority-boundaries, then test whether reflexive operations predict authorization, transmission, teaching strategy, and ethical reentry beyond doctrine and tradition membership.; difference: The current idea adds custody rule as a second axis beside boundary operation.; novelty impact: Very high reduction. This should be cross-indexed with authority-boundary work rather than published as a standalone discovery.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:53:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://voidnetwork.gr/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Idea-of-an-Anthropology-of-Islam-by-Talal-Asad.pdf: overlap: Close structural prior. Asad's discursive tradition foregrounds authorized instruction about correct practice, tradition, power, and the regulation of proper performance.; difference: Asad is not specifically modeling contemplative threshold operations or custody of freed attention.; novelty impact: High reduction for the authority-first and native-practice-first move.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:55:- Robert H. Sharf, Buddhist Modernism and the Rhetoric of Meditative Experience, DeepBlue record, https://deepblue.lib.umich.edu/items/25b7e9d4-d1f3-4280-8d53-95fa0b53db5c: overlap: Close pressure source. Sharf challenges the use of private meditative experience as a stable comparative unit and emphasizes rhetoric, institution, and authority around experience claims.; difference: Sharf does not offer a boundary-custody interaction test.; novelty impact: High reduction against treating the threshold as a direct phenomenological fact.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:56:- G. Victor Sogen Hori, Teaching and learning in the Rinzai Zen monastery, Cambridge record, https://www.cambridge.org/core/books/abs/teaching-and-learning-in-japan/teaching-and-learning-in-the-rinzai-zen-monastery/06E010651A6042E1FF3EC9BE242460D9: overlap: Close single-tradition prior. Hori shows ritual formalism and mystical insight working together in Rinzai training, which anticipates the link between method, testing, teacher authority, and transmission.; difference: It is not a cross-tradition two-axis model.; novelty impact: High reduction for Zen evidence and for any claim that verification architecture is newly noticed.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:59:- MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, raft simile, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html: overlap: Very close primary-text prior for boundary operation. The method is useful for crossing but not for holding onto afterward.; difference: The text is not a general comparative taxonomy and does not add custody recipients beyond the Dhamma's proper use.; novelty impact: High reduction for the method-validates-then-releases structure.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:60:- Heart Sutra, no attainment and reliance on Prajnaparamita, https://rctbt.org/heartsutra/: overlap: Very close primary-text prior for cancellation plus retained custody: no attainment, yet reliance on Prajnaparamita remains operative.; difference: The candidate generalizes the pattern and asks whether it predicts verification and reentry across traditions.; novelty impact: High reduction and a key anomaly against simple boundary categories.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:64:Unlike Asad, Lindbeck, Sharf, Hori, Pargament, VCE research, MN 22, the Heart Sutra, and prior Lumenary authority and custody ledgers, this idea's surviving distinct claim is a narrow interaction protocol: code boundary operation and custody rule independently, then test whether their interaction predicts held-out verification, teaching permission, warning, repair, and reentry patterns better than doctrine, tradition label, stage, institution, boundary alone, or custody alone. Without that split-source predictive gain, it is mostly a consolidation of prior work.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:68:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization identity, radical Other Power in Tannisho, inherited communal religion, and apophatic refusal in Dionysius.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:70:Why it strains the model: Dogen removes the gap between method and result, so there may be no threshold where boundary and custody can be assigned. Tannisho places decisive working in Amida's vow while warning against self-calculation, so calling entrusting a local custody handoff can reintroduce the self-power frame the text resists. Inherited religion may mature by continuity and ritual participation rather than by a discernible handoff. Dionysius places the divine Cause beyond affirmation and negation, which destabilizes God as a simple custody recipient.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:77:- If: Pairs sharing one axis but differing on the other should diverge predictably. Then: Cases with similar boundary cancellation but different custody rules, such as Heart Sutra reliance, Eckhartian Gelassenheit, and Madhyamaka non-positioning, should diverge in verification and reentry. Cases with similar vow or grace custody but different boundary operations should diverge in method retention and warning style. Weakens if: Pairs cluster mainly by broad tradition, institution, genre, teacher lineage, or language family rather than by boundary-custody pairing. Test surface: Matched primary-text pairs and held-out manuals, plus blind clustering against coded outcomes.
