./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:109:Structural translation: Boundary operation becomes how a method treats itself at maturity: retained protocol, self-undermining tool, embodied skill, or practice-identity. Custody rule becomes where authority and responsibility move after change: client agency, therapist, supervisor, group, protocol, medication, values, professional ethics, or embodied responsiveness.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:111:Prediction: Training systems that alter identity or attention should show distinct termination, supervision, relapse, and ethical-reentry patterns based on the interaction between method-boundary and custody. For example, a protocol that is later internalized should differ from one that is explicitly released, and both should differ when responsibility is held by client values, supervisor authority, group accountability, or professional ethics.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:121:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.42. The exact language is fresh, but both axes and much of the predictive burden are already present in prior Lumenary records: Method's Reckoning, Custody of Unclaimed Attention, Authority-Boundary Ecology, Custody and Receiving Surface, and related entry and support ledgers. External prior art also strongly anticipates the components: Asad and Lindbeck for native authority and grammar, Sharf and Katz-style contextualism for suspicion of experience-first comparison, Hori for Zen training and verification, Pargament for agency distribution, VCE for multidimensional contemplative difficulty coding, MN 22 for validated-then-released method, Heart Sutra for no-attainment plus reliance, Tannisho for Other Power custody, and Dogen for practice-realization anomaly. The surviving value is a bounded split-source interaction test, not a doctrine candidate or strong original discovery.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:129:- Add mandatory values for no-threshold, practice-realization, retained method, released method, self-undermining method, embodied method, radical Other Power, vow-held, grace-held, teacher-held, conduct-held, community-held, Prajnaparamita-held, no-custody-frame, continuous authorization, inherited practice, apophatic refusal, and undecidable.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:130:- Compare predictive value against Asad discursive tradition, Lindbeck grammar, Weberian authority, Sharf and Katz contextualism, Pargament agency styles, upaya pedagogy, VCE variables, institution type, teacher style, social ecology, clinical risk, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
./reviews/originality/2026-05-26-boundary-and-custody-at-the-threshold-c79517a2a7daa9cc.md:132:- Close-read MN 22, Heart Sutra, Dogen Genjokoan or Bendowa, Tannisho, Cloud of Unknowing, Dionysius Mystical Theology, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out source, and one Sufi fana or baqa source before further scoring.
./observations/codex/2026-05-26-agency-authority-calibration-at-the-handoff.md:11:Transformative practices should first be read through the practitioner's starting agency profile, then through staged handoff events in which capacities are confirmed, ownership is canceled, support is entrusted, or the claimant frame dissolves. The sequence matters: it should predict the practice's warnings, safeguards, repair practices, and non-fit cases. For over-claiming strivers, a practice may need to cancel ownership of a real capacity. For under-claiming people, especially those shaped by coercion, trauma, or denied authority, the first ethical move may be to confirm perception, rebuild boundaries, and permit agency before any surrender or dissolution language is introduced.
./observations/codex/2026-05-26-agency-authority-calibration-at-the-handoff.md:15:The proponent supplied a three-operation vocabulary, but located it too strongly at completion. The challenger supplied a staged handoff rubric, but did not fully develop cohort-gated agency calibration as the prior safety condition. The dialogue produced a candidate synthesis that treats authority transfer as one part of a broader agency-calibration grammar, with predictive and therapeutic constraints. This still needs an originality audit before any promotion.
