./runs/20260526-033741-claude-generate-a-new-original-cross-tradition-finding-/prompt.md:1250:Use LangGraph for the persistent recursive loop, OpenAI Deep Research or Responses API for cited research, LlamaIndex for ingestion, Qdrant for vector retrieval, and DuckDB or SQLite for structured local memory. Hermes can serve as a local worker model for cheaper extraction, clustering, and brainstorming, but should not be the only reasoning authority in v1.
